fields.description:
An error displayed where review diffs should be.

{noformat}
An error occured attempting to display this file.

java.lang.Exception: Not enough revisions to diff
{noformat}

Reproducable @ https://extranet.atlassian.com/crucible/cru/CR-FE-696

1.6.1 requires more permgen space compared to previous 1.5.* releases, hence customers are likely to get the following error (after upgrading or newly installing):

{noformat}
java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: PermGen space
{noformat}

Which can cause their server to crash or hang. 

The solution is simple:
{quote}
To avoid this in the future follow the steps detailed in the guide [Fix out of Memory Errors|http://confluence.atlassian.com/x/vADfCQ]. Scroll down "OutOfMemoryError: PermGen space" 
{quote}

However it is likely to cause an increase of Support cases typically marked as critical (as it causes the server to crash).
